description.content:
Confused about which package to buy? just message me :)

Having an attractive Nextjs Web App is very important so users spend most of their time on the website only if it's smooth

I am Ismail, A Professional Frontend Web App Developer providing reliable web services for custom web applications since 2017 and completed 500+ websites all across the globe.


Services I Offer:

  • Landing page in Nextjs
  • Convert your Reactjs web into Nextjs
  • Figma to Next js
  • Adobe xd to Nextjs 
  • PSD to Nextjs 
  • Use of tailwind CSS
  • Responsiveness across all devices
  • Cross Browser Compatible
  • Use of Typescripp as per requirement
  • Server Side Rendering 

Why me:

  • Top rated seller on Fiverr having a maximum of 5star reviews
  • Quality Work with standardized code
  • Keep you in the loop with daily updates
  • Reasonable Cost
  • Fast Delivery
  • Customer Support 
  • Clean code with proper commenting
  • Reusable component

Bonus:

I keep clients in the loop in the process of development, to deploy my work on a testing domain and clients can check from there and can share feedback along with the work and that's how I get satisfaction from clients.


You deserve the best, Feel free to place your order now

questionsAndAnswers.question: How do I get started on a project with you ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Simply reach out to me with your requirements, and I'll get back to you promptly. We'll discuss your project's details, timeline, and budget, and I'll provide you with a custom quote. Once we agree on the terms, we'll start working on your project right away.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What is the requirement to start Project?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Well, I need a Design File (PSD - Ai - Sketch - Figma - Xd) OR Your Inspiration Design of any Live Website on the Internet to begin the Project.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What's your GitHub profile?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
Here you go:
This is my username: ismail-programmer

questionsAndAnswers.question: How do you ensure client satisfaction for completed work?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I present live demos for the completed work, and offer revisions, Once the work is approved, only then do I send the delivery of the order.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will my website will be mobile friendly?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: For Sure, IF you want to make it responsive(mobile friendly) then you just need to mention that in your requirements with its design so I will make sure it will be good on mobile devices.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you convert Figma designs to Nextjs?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, you can share your Figma design and I can develop it into a pixel-perfect, responsive, Nextjs website.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What is covered in Revisions?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Revisions apply to unlimited changes/revisions in the decided scope of work in an order and do not apply to new development or new features that were not a part of the originally decided scope of work.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you host website after development on our domain?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: For Sure, If you need to make your website live, and you have domain and hosting purchased already then just mention this, and I will help in this but it will have some extra charges as well.
